Usage: set_socv_reporting_nsigma_multiplier [-help] [-view <list_of_views>] {[-setup <float>] [-hold <float>] [-transition <float>] }

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
-hold <float>             # Specifies the sigma multiplier for hold mode
                          # (float, optional)
-setup <float>            # Specifies the sigma multiplier for setup mode
                          # (float, optional)
-transition <float>       # Specifies the sigma multiplier for transition
                          # (float, optional)
-view <list_of_views>     # Apply the sigma multiplier factor to the specified
                          # list of analysis views. (string, optional)